this is my own personal game. just created for fun using my friends images. 
i was just learning pygame and wanted to make a game.

steps:
1) install from github
2) in cmd - > pip install -r requirements.txt
3) run space game BV.py or in cmd - > python space game BV.py
controls:
- left - j
- right - l
- down - k
- top - i
- shoot - space